---
title: Chinese Caramelised Pork Bowl with Garlic Rice, Rainbow Slaw & Fried Eggs
description: This bountiful bowl has "new favourite" written all over it! Our exceptional Sichuan garlic paste is the key ingredient, giving a delicious flavour kick to the pork mince. With tender rainbow veggies, an aromatic bed of garlic rice and a fried egg to top things off, it's a winner from start to finish.
